    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n2229" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">δέμας</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">δέμω</span>): <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">frame, build</span> of body; joined with
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">εἶδος, φυή</span>, and freq. with
          adjectives as acc. of specification, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μῑκρός,
            ἄριστος</span>, etc.—As adv., <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">like</span> (instar),
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μάρναντο δέμας πυρὸς αἰθομένοιο</span>,
            <i><span class="en">Il. 11.596</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
